---
// Lessi AI feature section — elevated full-width treatment
// Uses bg-primary text-primary-content to create the visual peak of the page
// Breaks out of the standard max-w-2xl column — rendered full-width from index.astro
---

<section aria-labelledby="lessi-heading" class="w-full bg-primary text-primary-content">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 py-14 space-y-5">
    <!-- Section label -->
    <div>
      <span class="inline-block border border-primary-content/40 text-primary-content/80 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full px-3 py-1">
        What I&apos;m Building
      </span>
    </div>

    <h2 id="lessi-heading" class="text-3xl font-bold">Lessi AI</h2>
    <p class="text-primary-content/70 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide">
      Co-Founder &amp; CTO
    </p>

    <p class="text-primary-content/90 leading-relaxed text-lg">
      <strong class="text-primary-content font-semibold">Lessi</strong> is an AI platform designed
      to help <strong class="text-primary-content font-semibold">special education teachers</strong>
      create high-quality instructional materials tailored to the needs of every student.
    </p>

    <p class="text-primary-content/80 leading-relaxed">
      The platform uses AI to generate and adapt lesson plans, assessments, reading passages,
      and instructional supports &mdash; all aligned with students&apos; IEPs, state and national
      standards, and evidence-based instructional practices.
    </p>

    <p class="text-primary-content/80 leading-relaxed">
      Lessi combines AI generation, structured educational content, and teacher workflows to
      dramatically reduce preparation time while improving instruction quality.
    </p>

    <div class="pt-2">
      <a
        href="https://www.lessi.ai"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn btn-sm border-primary-content/60 text-primary-content bg-transparent hover:bg-primary-content/15 hover:border-primary-content"
      >
        Visit Lessi AI
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/>
          <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/>
          <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
